4.htm |publisher=Yomiuri |date=19 September 2011}}</ref>\n\n'''Head coach:''' {{flagicon|NZL}} [[John Kirwan (rugby)|John Kirwan]]\n{{nat rs start}}\n{{nat rs player|pos=HK|name=[[Yusuke Aoki]]|age={{Birth date and age2|2011|9|9|1983|2|28|df=y}}|caps=21|club=[[Suntory Sungoliath]]|clubnat=Japan}}\n{{nat rs player|pos=HK|name=[[Shota Horie]]|age={{Birth date and age2|2011|9|9|1986|1|21|df=y}}|caps=14|club=[[Panasonic Wild Knights]]|clubnat=Japan}}\n{{nat rs player|pos=HK|name=[[Hiroki Yuhara]]|age={{Birth date and age2|2011|9|9|1984|1|21|df=y}}|caps=8|club=[[Toshiba Brave Lupus]]|clubnat=Japan}}\n{{nat rs player|pos=PR|name=[[Nozomu Fujita]]|age={{Birth date and age2|2011|9|9|1984|10|2|df=y}}|caps=10|club=[[Honda Heat]]|clubnat=Japan}}\n{{nat rs player|pos=PR|name=[[Kensuke Hatakeyama]]|age={{Birth date and age2|2011|9|9|1985|8|2|df=y}}|caps=23|club=[[Suntory Sungoliath]]|clubnat=Japan}}\n{{nat rs player|pos=PR|name=[[Hisateru Hirashima]]|age={{Birth date and age2|2011|9|9|1983|1|15|df=y}}|caps=24|club=[[Kobelco Steelers]]|clubnat=Japan}}\n{{nat rs player|pos=PR|name=[[Naoki Kawamata]]|age={{Birth date and age2|2011|9|9|1985|10|31|df=y}}|caps=17|club=[[Panasonic Wild Knights]]|clubnat=Japan}}\n{{nat rs player|pos=LK|name=[[Toshizumi Kitagawa]]|age={{Birth date and age2|2011|9|9|1981|2|7|df=y}}|caps=37|club=[[Toyota Verblitz]]|clubnat=Japan}}\n{{nat rs player|pos=LK|name=[[Yuji Kitagawa]]|age={{Birth date and age2|2011|9|9|1986|8|11|df=y}}|caps=5|club=[[Panasonic Wild Knights]]|clubnat=Japan}}\n{{nat rs player|pos=LK|name=[[Hitoshi Ono]]|age={{Birth date and age2|2011|9|9|1978|5|6|df=y}}|caps=51|club=[[Toshiba Brave Lupus]]|clubnat=Japan}}\n{{nat rs player|pos=LK|name=[[Luke Thompson (rugby player)|Luke Thompson]]|age={{Birth date and age2|2011|9|9|1981|4|16|df=y}}|caps=34|club=[[Kintetsu Liners]]|clubnat=Japan}}\n{{nat rs player|pos=FL|name=[[Takashi Kikutani]] ([[Captain (sports)|c]])|age={{Birth date and age2|2011|9|9|1980|2|24|df=y}}|caps=44|club=[[Toyota Verblitz